Backpacks & Buzz Cuts: Blasdell’s Back to School Event. 

@dmtcares in partnership with First Choice Cleaners will be donating the following: 

100 backpacks, each individually filled with: 

1) One-subject notebook
(1) Pack of 100 index cards
(4) Two pocket folders
(3) Glue sticks
(5) No. 2 pencils
(1) Pencil Case
(1) Plastic ruler

But that’s not all! @mg_fades99 will be providing FREE #buzzcuts to kids ages 15 and under.

-
First annual “Backpacks & Buzzcuts” event in Blasdell, NY. 
We gave away 100+ backpacks with school supplies, Basketballs, Footballs, Soccer Balls, and had Hotdogs & Hamburgers🎒💈

Every year we do at least one big charity event to help out the community and those in need. 

Shoutout to everyone who helped:
DMT Cares @dmtcares @dylantoole 
First Choice Cleaners @big_homie_bollinger 
MG Fades/Heartfelt Cutz @mg_fades99 @heartfeltcutz
